{"data":[{"date":"06:15 30/07","title":"R\u1eddi Juventus, Buffon mi\u1ec5n lu\u00f4n b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 Ronaldo","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/30/roi-juventus-buffon-mien-luon-binh-luan-ve-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Buffon kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 Juventus v\u00e0 Ronaldo. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n l\u00e3o l\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a Bianconeri gi\u1edd ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n theo d\u00f5i h\u1ecd thi \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>B\u00e0ng quan v\u1edbi Ronaldo</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y, HLV Max Allegri \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c: \u201cS\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Ronaldo g\u00e2y h\u1ea1i cho Juventus\u201d. Theo \u00f4ng, \u0111ang c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i Juventus v\u00e0 d\u1eabn t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 ch\u1ee7 quan trong \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi 2018/19.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e2u h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 Juventus s\u1edf h\u1eefu Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mang t\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a CLB. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Gianluigi Buffon kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 Juventus v\u00e0 Ronaldo. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 40 tu\u1ed5i r\u1eddi Juve sau 17 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1edbi Paris Saint-Germain d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do h\u00e8 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 theo c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Buffon kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 Juventus v\u00e0 Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Buffon kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 Juventus v\u00e0 Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/Buffon-va-Ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Buffon kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 Juventus v\u00e0 Ronaldo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u1eefng g\u00ec Juve \u0111ang l\u00e0m b\u00e2y gi\u1edd l\u00e0 c\u00e1i g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00f4i v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch m\u1ed9t kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3\u201d, Buffon n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean. \u201cJuventus l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t CLB tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 PSG v\u00e0 t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. H\u1ecd s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>L\u00fd gi\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c t\u1edbi PSG</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c b\u1ed5 sung Cristiano Ronaldo v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro t\u1eeb Real Madrid kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh tham v\u1ecdng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League c\u1ee7a Juventus sau 22 n\u0103m. Danh hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e8m kh\u00e1t b\u1edfi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 CLB ch\u00e2u \u00c2u n\u00e0o. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u1ef1u sao Juve kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1eefng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1eeba qua kh\u00f4ng li\u00ean quan g\u00ec t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c anh r\u1eddi Italia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u00dd ngh\u0129a c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn n\u00e0y l\u00e0 b\u1edfi t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao nh\u1ea5t\u201d, Buffon n\u00f3i th\u00eam. \u201cH\u01a1n n\u1eefa, t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n b\u1ecb k\u00edch th\u00edch b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t CLB \u0111\u1ea7y tham v\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 PSG. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng sau 40 n\u0103m \u1edf Italia, s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap t\u00f4i ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p b\u1edfi t\u00f4i \u0111ang b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi m\u1edbi.\u201d<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Juventus tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/juventus-ban-3-cau-thu-mua-pogba-172-192247.html\">Juventus b\u00e1n 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 mua sao kh\u1ee7ng MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pep-guardiola-len-tieng-ve-kha-nang-chieu-mo-sao-juventus-172-192204.html\">Pep Guardiola l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/allegri-su-co-mat-cua-ronaldo-gay-hai-cho-juventus-176-192193.html\">Allegri: \u201cS\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Ronaldo g\u00e2y h\u1ea1i cho Juventus\u201d</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/bld-mu-ngan-can-mourinho-chieu-mo-sandro-172-192120.html\">BL\u0110 MU ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Mourinho chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao kh\u1ee7ng Juventus</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4800","checkdouble":"192279"},{"date":"20:01 29/07","title":"Th\u1eafng nh\u1eb9 Campuchia, HLV \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u00f3i g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/29/thang-nhe-campuchia-hlv-doi-tuyen-u16-viet-nam-noi-gi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U16 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng kh\u00e1 nh\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1n v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u00e1ng gi\u1ec1ng Campuchia. V\u00e0 HLV V\u0169 H\u1ed3ng Vi\u1ec7t \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y?</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Campuch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Campuch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/hlv-u16-viet-nam-noi-gi-khi-de-campuchia-gay-kho-khan-lon1532863898.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV&nbsp;U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Campuchia</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 29/7, \u0110T U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U16 \u0110N\u00c1 2018 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 U16 Campuchia. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o v\u00e0 tung ra v\u00f4 s\u1ed1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea1n. Tuy nhi\u00ean trong m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y m\u00e0 c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ecf ra v\u00f4 duy\u00ean, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV V\u0169 H\u1ed3ng Vi\u1ec7t ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 s\u00edt sao.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i t\u00e2m s\u1ef1: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u1ebd ra ph\u1ea3i ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng h\u01a1n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i h\u00f4m nay c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u01b0a thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00ec l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean n\u00ean c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb h\u01a1i b\u1ecb c\u0103ng c\u1ee9ng v\u1ec1 t\u00e2m l\u00fd n\u00ean ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thanh tho\u00e1t c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e1p.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn Campuchia \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n. H\u1ecd \u0111i b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 l\u00fang t\u00fang khi ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf cho Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 g\u1eb7p Timor Leste&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ngu\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Vi\u1ec7t Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo. V\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 31/7 t\u1edbi h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Timor Leste tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng U16 Indonesia (2/8), Philippines (4/8) v\u00e0 Myanmar (6/8).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;&#10;line-height:115%;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4799","checkdouble":"192266"},{"date":"21:26 29/07","title":"\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u201ch\u1ecdc l\u1ecfm b\u00e0i t\u1ee7\" c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/29/dt-olympic-viet-nam-hoc-lom-bai-tu-cua-nguoi-anh-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1eeb l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, HLV Park Hang Seo c\u0169ng \u0111ang cho \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</h2><h2>HLV Park Hang Seo&nbsp;s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng 'b\u00e0i t\u1ee7' c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh cho&nbsp;<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam&nbsp;</span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t phong c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c kh\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m ph\u1ea7n hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. Theo \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u00e0nh h\u00e0ng d\u1ecdc v\u00e0 khi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c treo v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd di chuy\u1ec3n theo c\u00e1c h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong vi\u1ec7c theo k\u00e8m.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u1ecdc l\u1ecfm b\u00e0i t\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh t\u1ea1i World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u1ecdc l\u1ecfm b\u00e0i t\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh t\u1ea1i World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/3796019017954803772340125875540635594784768newiy-crop-15327648207251944130715.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Park Hang Seo b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 cao to c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi hai l\u1ea7n, \u0110T Anh ghi b\u00e0n t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do HLV Park Hang Seo mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp chi\u1ec1u qua 28/7, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 t\u1ea1i \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n theo &quot;mi\u1ebfng \u0111\u00e1nh&quot; n\u00e0y. B\u00e0i t\u1eadp m\u1edbi \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp trung cao \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00edch nghi v\u00e0 l\u00e0m quen \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean c\u00e1c pha \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fac n\u00e0y, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u cao t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 gi\u1ecfi kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, Ti\u1ebfn Linh, \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh hay V\u0103n H\u1eadu. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, n\u1ebfu luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp th\u00e0nh th\u1ee5c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p n\u00e0y, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch, \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd r\u00e8n qu\u00e2n \u1edf Trung t\u00e2m PVF cho \u0111\u1ebfn 31/8 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho gi\u1ea3i T\u1ee9 H\u00f9ng di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00ean s\u00e2n M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 3 t\u1edbi 7/8 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 U23 Palestine, U23 Oman v\u00e0 U23 Uzbekistan. C\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec1u di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h30 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 d\u1ecbp c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y Park ch\u1ed1t danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c 20 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-tre-dt-olympic-viet-nam-tu-tin-se-duoc-thay-park-giu-lai-168-192239.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/9/15/taninhu19.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-tre-dt-olympic-viet-nam-tu-tin-se-duoc-thay-park-giu-lai-168-192239.html\">Sao tr\u1ebb \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ef1 tin s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i</span><br />\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp chi\u1ec1u 28/7, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Hu\u1ef3nh T\u1ea5n Sinh t\u1ef1 tin cho bi\u1ebft anh s\u1ebd th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang Seo gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-chinh-thuc-chia-tay-cau-thu-dau-tien-168-192236.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/29/dt-olympic-viet-nam-chinh-thuc-chia-tay-cau-thu-dau-tien.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-chinh-thuc-chia-tay-cau-thu-dau-tien-168-192236.html\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean</span><br />\r\nC\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh khi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n Phong H\u1ed3ng Duy d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t n\u1eb7ng trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp chi\u1ec1u...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:&#10;\" new=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4798","checkdouble":"192269"},{"date":"21:48 29/07","title":"\u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vinh danh tr\u00ean b\u00e1o n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/16/dt-u23-viet-nam-lai-duoc-vinh-danh-tren-bao-nuoc-ngoai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u1edd FOX Sports m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft cho r\u1eb1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia n\u00ean l\u1ea5y c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng t\u1eeb \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018.</h2><h2>\u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vinh danh tr\u00ean b\u00e1o n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vinh danh tr\u00ean b\u00e1o n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vinh danh tr\u00ean b\u00e1o n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/lich-thi-dau-u23-viet-nam-giai-tu-hung-vff-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>FOX Sports cho r\u1eb1ng Indonesia c\u1ea7n h\u1ecdc theo \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd b\u00e1o th\u1ec3 thao n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i FOX Sports m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018. B\u1eb1ng ch\u1ee9ng l\u00e0 t\u1edd b\u00e1o n\u00e0y cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Indonesia c\u1ea7n l\u1ea5y c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng t\u1eeb\u00a0nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn binh \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf\u00a0n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">FOX Sports vi\u1ebft: \"Ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu Indonesia \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n v\u1ebd l\u1ea1i b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed3 gi\u1ea3i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea1i ASIAD\u2026 \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 thao ch\u00e2u \u00c1 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1edbn v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi ch\u00e2u \u00c1, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Indonesia \u0111ang r\u1ea5t hy v\u1ecdng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u \u1edf ASIAD 18. Vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 gi\u00e0nh huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng hay kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eb3ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111i\u1ec1u qu\u00e1 quan tr\u1ecdng, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfn c\u00e0ng s\u00e2u c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 l\u1edbn lao c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Indonesia, \u0111\u1ec3 mang l\u1ea1i ni\u1ec1m vui cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Indonesia s\u1ebd c\u1ea5t c\u00e1nh trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m qu\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y trong th\u00e1ng 1 t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Trung Qu\u1ed1c. Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1ed1n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i ti\u1ebfn t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft. Tr\u00ean su\u1ed1t ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp khi c\u00f3 h\u00e0ng tri\u1ec7u ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ed5 ra \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ed5 v\u0169 cho h\u1ecd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Indonesia th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f4ng d\u00e2n h\u01a1n Vi\u1ec7t Nam, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 Indonesia t\u00e1i l\u1eadp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch nh\u01b0 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng\u2026\u201d. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay, n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 d\u1ec5 c\u00f9ng L\u00e0o, Hong Kong, \u0110\u00e0i Loan v\u00e0 Palestine. N\u1ebfu thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00fang kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f9ng l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng V\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea3o ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn xa v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00e0o t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-hoc-lom-bai-tu-cua-nguoi-anh-tai-world-cup-2018-168-192269.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/29/dt-olympic-viet-nam-hoc-lom-bai-tu-cua-nguoi-anh-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-hoc-lom-bai-tu-cua-nguoi-anh-tai-world-cup-2018-168-192269.html\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u201ch\u1ecdc l\u1ecfm b\u00e0i t\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1eeb l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, HLV Park Hang Seo c\u0169ng \u0111ang cho \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4797","checkdouble":"192270"},{"date":"22:43 29/07","title":"Neymar s\u1ebd s\u1edbm tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/29/neymar-se-som-tro-lai-sau-tham-hoa-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u00f9 h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, nh\u01b0ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng PSG \u2013 HLV Tuchel chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Neymar v\u1edbi ni\u1ec1m tin r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nTuchel kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Neymar s\u1ebd s\u1edbm tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1eabn trong th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i sau khi tr\u1ea3i qua k\u1ef3 World Cup kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y vui v\u1ebb, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Neymar v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh h\u1ebft l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, HLV Thomas Tuchel cho bi\u1ebft:<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 Neymar c\u1ea7n th\u00eam b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c n\u00e0o so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Brazil mu\u1ed1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n gi\u00fap Neymar tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i h\u1ebft m\u1ee9c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;B\u1ecf qua s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Neymar s\u1ebd bi\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i \u0111au th\u00e0nh h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 bi\u1ebft l\u00e0m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. B\u1ea1n lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng th\u1eed th\u00e1ch trong th\u1ec3 thao, v\u00e0 Neymar s\u1ebd s\u1edbm tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Tuchel chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Neymar tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi\" title=\"Neymar\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/neymar-se-som-tro-lai-sau-tham-hoa-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Tuchel chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Neymar tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nTr\u1ea3i qua m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Ph\u00e1p, si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi 26 b\u00e0n sau 29 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n, gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t Ligue 1. Anh g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 2, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng Selecao khi b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i t\u1eeb t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 PSG sau nh\u1eefng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, b\u1ecf ngo\u00e0i tai nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00e0 tin \u0111\u1ed3n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1edbi Real Madrid, Neymar s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia m\u1edbi. V\u00e0 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u00e2n HLV Tuchel chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Neymar, anh \u0111ang c\u00f3 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nhanh nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-phap/alves-bao-ve-neymar-vi-thoi-an-va-197-191719.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/12/alves-bao-ve-neymar-vi-thoi-an-va.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-phap/alves-bao-ve-neymar-vi-thoi-an-va-197-191719.html\">Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 l\u0169 kh\u00f4ng n\u00e3o m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Neymar</span><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng x\u1ea5u m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Brazil t\u1ea1o ra t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t leo thang, v\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Dani Alves l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Neymar tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t nh\u1eefng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/neymar-duoc-khuyen-nen-tu-bo-nghiep-cau-thu-va-chon-nghe-dien-vien-421-190281.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/neymar-duoc-khuyen-nen-tu-bo-nghiep-cau-thu-va-chon-nghe-dien-vien.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/neymar-duoc-khuyen-nen-tu-bo-nghiep-cau-thu-va-chon-nghe-dien-vien-421-190281.html\">Neymar \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean n\u00ean t\u1eeb b\u1ecf nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 ch\u1ecdn ngh\u1ec1 di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u00e1ng x\u1ea5u h\u1ed5 trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Mexico 2-0, ng\u00f4i sao Brazil \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch tr\u00ean to\u00e0n th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u00fd ki\u1ebfn v\u1ec1 h\u00ecnh...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4796","checkdouble":"192273"},{"date":"19:51 29/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 29/7: V\u1eeba sang Man City, bom t\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/29/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-297-vua-sang-man-city-bom-tan-da-dinh-chan-thuong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 29/7.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nV\u1eeba sang Man City, bom t\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi Bayern Munich v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Riyad Mahrez c\u1ee7a Man City \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb thay ra ngay t\u1eeb ph\u00fat 28. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y Man xanh \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eafng l\u1ea1i H\u00f9m x\u00e1m v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-2. HLV Pep Guardiola cho bi\u1ebft v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 t nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Mahrez, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 g\u00e2n kheo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 297 Bom t\u1ea5n Man City d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 297 Bom t\u1ea5n Man City d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/mah.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 29/7: Mahrez d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Juve b\u00e1n 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 mua l\u1ea1i Pogba<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 l\u1ea1i ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ngay h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng do \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n Cristiano Ronaldo, Juventus bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n b\u1edbt \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh. Theo \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd thu l\u1ea1i s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c b\u00e1n Gonzalo Higuain, Miralem Pjanic v\u00e0 Daniele Rugani, \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 v\u00e0 tr\u1ea3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng cho Pogba.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea nh\u1eafm tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Arsenal<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eb1m t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ef1 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, The Blues \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Aaron Ramsey. Hi\u1ec7n nay, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 12 th\u00e1ng v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7, v\u00e0 Chelsea mu\u1ed1n t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i khi Ramsey v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t vi\u1ec7c gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool ra gi\u00e1 h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Divock Origi, c\u00e1i t\u00ean b\u1ecb qu\u00ean l\u00e3ng t\u1ea1i Liverpool \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 26 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, v\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd ra \u0111i ngay m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, HLV Jurgen Klopp nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Daniel Sturridge \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho Roberto Firmino.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien dao Divock Origi\" title=\"tien dao Divock Origi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/8/26/Roi-Liverpool,-tien-dao-Divock-Origi-se-di-dau-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 29/7: Origi s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nBarca chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb chia tay ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng World Cup<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina, ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Camp Nou t\u1eeb k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng, \u0111ang tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng r\u1eddi CLB. Hi\u1ec7n nay, c\u00f3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Premier League r\u1ea5t quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Everton h\u1ecfi mua 27 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, v\u00e0 Man United v\u1edbi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn trung v\u1ec7 Colombia s\u1ebd ra \u0111i, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 anh s\u1ebd l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n&nbsp;<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-da-voi-cac-dong-doi-the-nay-sanchez-khong-tuc-moi-la-la-172-192260.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/29/mourinho-da-voi-cac-dong-doi-the-nay-sanchez-khong-tuc-moi-la-la.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-da-voi-cac-dong-doi-the-nay-sanchez-khong-tuc-moi-la-la-172-192260.html\">Mourinho: \u0110\u00e1 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i th\u1ebf n\u00e0y, Sanchez kh\u00f4ng t\u1ee9c m\u1edbi l\u00e0 l\u1ea1</span><br>\r\nHLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Sanchez sau khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile t\u1ecf ra v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng b\u1ef1c t\u1ee9c \u1edf tr\u1eadn thua cay \u0111\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Man United tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool v\u1eeba qua.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-man-city-phong-do-cua-pogba-khien-cac-chuyen-gia-phai-im-mom-172-192231.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/29/sao-man-city-phong-do-cua-pogba-khien-cac-chuyen-gia-phai-im-mom.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-man-city-phong-do-cua-pogba-khien-cac-chuyen-gia-phai-im-mom-172-192231.html\">Sao Man City: &ldquo;Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Pogba khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia ph\u1ea3i im m\u1ed3m&rdquo;</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i CLB, nh\u01b0ng tr\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Benjamin Mendy ca ng\u1ee3i Pogba \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p &ndash; TTVN</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4795","checkdouble":"192265"},{"date":"05:51 30/07","title":"Gi\u1eefa Messi v\u00e0 Ronaldo, Simeone ch\u1ecdn ai xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc h\u01a1n?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/giua-messi-va-ronaldo-simeone-chon-ai-xuat-sac-hon.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Diego Simeone ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Messi v\u00e0 Ronaldo. \u00d4ng cho r\u1eb1ng trong m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao, Lionel Messi l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00edch \u1ee9ng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Cu\u1ed9c tranh c\u00e3i Messi v\u00e0 Ronaldo</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSu\u1ed1t c\u1ea3 th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 qua, cu\u1ed9c so k\u00e8 gi\u1eefa Lionel Messi v\u00e0 Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m d\u1eady s\u00f3ng l\u00e0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u00e3 chia nhau m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi 5 Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng nh\u01b0 minh ch\u1ee9ng cho s\u1ef1 th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd trong m\u00f4n th\u1ec3 thao vua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c tranh c\u00e3i gi\u1eefa Messi v\u00e0 Ronaldo ai l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng vang l\u00ean. M\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 quan \u0111i\u1ec3m ri\u00eang khi\u1ebfn c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n k\u00e9o d\u00e0i nh\u01b0 v\u00f4 t\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Diego Simeone ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Messi v\u00e0 Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Diego Simeone ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Messi v\u00e0 Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/giua-messi-va-ronaldo-simeone-chon-ai-xuat-sac-hon.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Simeone ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Messi v\u00e0 Ronaldo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi HLV Diego Simeone, m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n ghi h\u00ecnh cho bi\u1ebft \u00f4ng th\u00edch Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n sau tr\u1eadn thua 3-0 c\u1ee7a Argentina tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t d\u1ecbp tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n, Simeone ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Messi v\u00e0 Ronaldo. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina \u0111\u00ednh ch\u00ednh r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Messi s\u1ebd n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt h\u01a1n Ronaldo khi bao quanh l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, khi b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n l\u00e0 Ronaldo. \u201cN\u1ebfu ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecdn gi\u1eefa Messi v\u00e0 Ronaldo, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ch\u1ecdn Messi\u201d, Simeone n\u00f3i. \u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn Ronaldo \u1edf trong \u0111o\u1ea1n video, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c tr\u00f2 chuy\u1ec7n gi\u1eefa t\u00f4i v\u00e0 tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd Atletico, German Burgos.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cKhi t\u00f4i n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Messi v\u00e0 Ronaldo, \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i quan \u0111i\u1ec3m ai l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eadp t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 h\u1ecd cho m\u1ed9t CLB b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng, v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng, Ronaldo c\u00f3 l\u1ebd s\u1ebd ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p h\u01a1n. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi Messi, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bao quanh b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd h\u01a1n Ronaldo.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Messi v\u00e0 Ronaldo tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/allegri-su-co-mat-cua-ronaldo-gay-hai-cho-juventus-176-192193.html\">Allegri: \u201cS\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Ronaldo g\u00e2y h\u1ea1i cho Juventus\u201d</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/cristiano-ronaldo-roi-real-madrid-khep-lai-18-nam-ky-nguyen-bong-vang-180-192169.html\">Cristiano Ronaldo r\u1eddi Real Madrid: Kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i 18 n\u0103m k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/neymar-va\u0300-messi-hit-khoi-ronaldo-ve-thu-nhap-tren-instagram-188-192144.html\">Neymar va\u0300 Messi 'h\u00edt kh\u00f3i' Ronaldo v\u1ec1 thu nh\u1eadp tr\u00ean Instagram</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/danh-sach-cau-thu-hay-nhat-nam-cua-fifa-mbappe-sanh-vai-cung-ronaldo-messi-184-191953.html\">Danh s\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hay nh\u1ea5t n\u0103m c\u1ee7a FIFA: Mbappe s\u00e1nh vai c\u00f9ng Ronaldo, Messi</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4794","checkdouble":"192278"},{"date":"06:39 30/07","title":"B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i \u201cth\u01b0\u01a1ng binh\u201d Barca b\u1ecb tr\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 CLB","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/30/bo-doi-thuong-binh-barca-bi-tra-ve-clb.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Denis Suarez v\u00e0 Andre Gomes d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 s\u1edbm tr\u1edf t\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha t\u1eeb tour du \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 chi ti\u1ebft h\u01a1n. Ch\u00ednh Barcelona \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Suarez v\u00e0 Gomes ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u00e0o s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua (29/7), Barcelona tr\u1ea3i qua tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u00e0u c\u1ea3m x\u00fac v\u1edbi Tottenham t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup tr\u00ean n\u01b0\u1edbc M\u1ef9. H\u1ecd d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh 2-0 song b\u1ecb g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a v\u00e0o n\u1eeda sau hi\u1ec7p 2. Sau c\u00f9ng, Barca v\u1eabn gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 5-3 tr\u00ean lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc r\u1eb1ng Denis Suarez v\u00e0 Andre Gomes d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, khi\u1ebfn chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Barca b\u1ecb lu m\u1edd. H\u1ecd l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t r\u1eddi s\u00e2n c\u00e1c ph\u00fat 22 v\u00e0 26 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Carles Perez v\u00e0 Ricard Puig.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Denis Suarez v\u00e0 Andre Gomes d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 s\u1edbm tr\u1edf t\u1ea1i TBN h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Denis Suarez v\u00e0 Andre Gomes d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 s\u1edbm tr\u1edf t\u1ea1i TBN h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/Suarez-va-Gomes.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Denis Suarez v\u00e0 Andre Gomes d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn, HLV Ernesto Valverde \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a International Champions Cup c\u1ee7a Suarez v\u00e0 Gomes.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o ng\u1eafn m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Barca x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Suarez v\u00e0 Gomes \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb Los Angeles, M\u1ef9 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha. \u201cDenis Suarez v\u00e0 Andre Gomes s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Barcelona t\u1eeb Los Angeles v\u00e0 c\u00f3 c\u00e1c b\u00e0i ki\u1ec3m tra t\u1ea1i trung t\u00e2m Ciutat Esportiva \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 chi ti\u1ebft m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng\u201d,<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1eadt tr\u00f9ng h\u1ee3p khi c\u1ea3 Suarez v\u00e0 Gomes \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ecb Barca thanh l\u00fd trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia \u0111ang xem x\u00e9t nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eedi t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Camp Nou cho b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/andre-gomes-muon-toi-tottenham-172-191411.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/12/6/andre-gomes-muon-toi-tottenham.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/andre-gomes-muon-toi-tottenham-172-191411.html\">Sao th\u1ea5t s\u1ee7ng c\u1ee7a Barca mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1 c\u00f9ng Harry Kane t\u1ea1i Premier League</span><br>\r\n<span>Ng\u00f4i sao b\u1ecb th\u1ea5t s\u1ee7ng t\u1ea1i Barca, Andre Gomes d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh gia nh\u1eadp Tottenham, theo th\u00f4ng tin t\u1eeb t\u1edd Mundo Deportivo.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay c\u1ea3 khi Andres Iniesta v\u00e0 Paulinho l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t r\u1eddi Barca h\u00e8 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1edbi ch\u00e2u \u00c1 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng (l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t Vissel Kobe v\u00e0 Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u Evergrande), Suarez v\u00e0 Gomes v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, Blaugrana nh\u1eafm b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Miralem Pjanic (Juventus) v\u00e0 Frenkie de Jong (Ajax).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Barca \u0111\u00e3 mua g\u1ea5p Arthur t\u1eeb Gremio v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 40 tri\u1ec7u Euro d\u00f9 d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1edbi n\u0103m 2019 m\u1edbi mang anh v\u1ec1. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil, nh\u1eefng Clement Lenglet v\u00e0 Malcom t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Sevilla v\u00e0 Bordeaux c\u0169ng l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Barcelona tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-nang-gia-hoi-mua-mina-len-35-trieu-bang-172-192242.html\">MU n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i Barca l\u00ean 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/barca-vs-tottenham-tran-dau-icc-2018-ngay-hom-nay-372-192222.html\">Barca 2-2 (pen 5-3) Tottenham (KT): L\u1ee9a m\u0103ng non La Masia th\u1eafng b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh sau lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/lenglet-tuyen-bo-san-sang-chien-dau-o-barca-180-192211.html\">Lenglet tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-barcelona-tuyen-bo-se-no-them-bom-tan-180-192202.html\">HLV Barcelona tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd n\u1ed5 th\u00eam bom t\u1ea5n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/everton-tien-gan-toi-chu-ky-lucas-digne-180-192181.html\">Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Mina, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u201ch\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\u201d Barca thanh l\u00fd \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4793","checkdouble":"192281"},{"date":"20:58 29/07","title":"Arsenal v\u1ee1 m\u1ed9ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/arsenal-vo-mong-vu-steven-nzonzi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1eb3ng, CLB Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Steven N'Zonzi t\u1eeb Sevilla trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>Arsenal v\u1ee1 m\u1ed9ng v\u1ee5 Steven N'Zonzi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal v\u1ee1 m\u1ed9ng v\u1ee5 Steven NZonzi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Arsenal v\u1ee1 m\u1ed9ng v\u1ee5 Steven NZonzi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/Arsenal-vo-mong-vu-Steven-NZonzi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Arsenal b\u1ecb Roma n\u1eabng tay tr\u00ean v\u1ee5 Steven N'Zonzi</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m nay, t\u00e2n HLV Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m Lucas Torreira t\u1eeb Sampdoria.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n TBN v\u1ec1 ch\u01b0a d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf \u0111\u00f3. L\u00fac n\u00e0y \u00f4ng v\u1eabn \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n mang v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Emirates m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. V\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Emery nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi l\u00e0 Steven N\u2019Zonzi, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng t\u1ea1i CLB Sevilla.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u2019Zonzi n\u0103m nay 29 tu\u1ed5i, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 kh\u00e1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Trong 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Sevilla, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n 136 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 8 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. S\u1edf h\u1eefu chi\u1ec1u cao l\u00ean t\u1edbi 1m97, \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Emirates c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a HLV Emery s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh khi m\u00e0 Sevilla d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111ang c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch b\u00e1n N\u2019Zonzi sang Roma. Theo truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Italy, Roma \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Steven N\u2019Zonzi v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1edf d\u0129 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Monchi \u2013 ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eebng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1i Sevilla v\u00e0 gi\u1edd \u0111ang l\u00e0 Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao t\u1ea1i Roma. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00ednh nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt n\u00e0y l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0a N\u2019Zonzi v\u1ec1 Sevilla v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2015.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edd b\u00e1o t\u1ea1i \u00dd c\u0169ng cho bi\u1ebft sau khi c\u00f9ng tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018, Steven N\u2019Zonzi \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edfng k\u00ec ngh\u1ec9 \u1edf M\u1ef9, n\u01a1i Roma \u0111ang tham d\u1ef1 tour du \u0111\u1ea5u. V\u00ec v\u1eady, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u00e0 Arsenal theo \u0111u\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf v\u00e0 h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Eusebio Di Francesco t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-297-vua-sang-man-city-bom-tan-da-dinh-chan-thuong-184-192265.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/29/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-297-vua-sang-man-city-bom-tan-da-dinh-chan-thuong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-297-vua-sang-man-city-bom-tan-da-dinh-chan-thuong-184-192265.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 29/7: V\u1eeba sang Man City, bom t\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</span><br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 29/7.</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4792","checkdouble":"192267"},{"date":"22:08 29/07","title":"B\u1ea1n th\u00e2n Neymar mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed t\u1ea1i Spurs","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/19/ban-than-neymar-muon-lam-nen-lich-su-tai-spurs.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi Premier League, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Lucas Moura h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng Tottenham, qua nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nMoura quy\u1ebft l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i l\u00e0m quen tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb t\u1ea1i PSG (v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n l\u00fd do b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Neymar), ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Lucas Moura \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ra \u0111i t\u00ecm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi. Anh \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n sang Tottenham v\u00e0o k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng v\u1eeba qua v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, v\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng hi\u1ec3u bi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 anh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Khi t\u00f4i c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Brazil, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n sang ch\u00e2u \u00c2u thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 l\u00fac n\u00e0y. T\u1ea1i Brazil, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 b\u1ea1o l\u1ef1c, \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lucas Moura h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng Tottenham\" title=\"Lucas Moura cua Tottenham\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/2/Truoc-vong-26-Premier-League-Man-chao-hang-cua-bom-tan-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lucas Moura h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng Tottenham</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i l\u1edbn l\u00ean \u1edf m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 r\u1ea5t ngh\u00e8o. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 lu\u00f4n t\u00e2m ni\u1ec7m ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, ph\u1ea3i tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 theo \u0111u\u1ed5i \u01b0\u1edbc m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, Premier League, Champions League. \u0110\u1ebfn gi\u1edd, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u00f3n qu\u00e0 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi t\u1eeb Ch\u00faa.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u hay nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c ra s\u00e2n v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed t\u1ea1i Tottenham. \u0110\u00e2t l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn v\u00e0 t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui khi chuy\u1ec3n sang Spurs. T\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 di\u1ec7u, gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0 l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;6 th\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 th\u1eddi gian t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edbi, l\u00e0m qu\u00ean v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. B\u00e2y gi\u1edd, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh. Nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng&rdquo; &ndash; Lucas Moura h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng Tottenham.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tottenham-gap-kho-vu-mua-grealish-172-192258.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/29/tottenham-gap-kho-vu-mua-grealish.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tottenham-gap-kho-vu-mua-grealish-172-192258.html\">Tottenham g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 v\u1ee5 mua sao h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t</span><br>\r\nTottenham g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 v\u1ee5 mua Grealish. CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n Aston Villa c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh 23 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n nh\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi sau khi \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft xong b\u00e0i to\u00e1n t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/zaha-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-172-192254.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/13/zaha-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/zaha-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-172-192254.html\">M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng b\u00e1o tin vui cho Tottenham v\u00e0 Chelsea</span><br>\r\nWilfried Zaha n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Crystal Palace \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-barca-22-pen-53-tottenham-icc-2018-329-192246.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/28/video-tong-hop-barca-22-pen-53-tottenham-icc-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-barca-22-pen-53-tottenham-icc-2018-329-192246.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Barca 2-2 (pen 5-3) Tottenham (ICC 2018)</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London san b\u1eb1ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 sau khi v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2-0, \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh g\u1ed3m ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn c\u00e1c g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh t\u1eeb l\u00f2 La Masia \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4791","checkdouble":"192271"},{"date":"22:22 29/07","title":"Pochettino kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng mua l\u1ea1i Gareth Bale","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/27/pochettino-khang-dinh-khong-mua-lai-gareth-bale.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p, nh\u01b0ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y HLV Pochettini kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Tottenham kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn Gareth Bale, v\u00e0 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng mua ng\u01b0\u1eddi.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nGareth Bale kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1ec1 Tottenham<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ee7 m\u1ecdi danh hi\u1ec7u t\u1ea1i Real Madrid, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111i t\u00ecm th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Man United, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Tottenham Hotspur \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1ec1 ng\u00f4i sao 29 tu\u1ed5i, tuy nhi\u00ean HLV Pochettino \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 n\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf&rdquo; &ndash; HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina cho bi\u1ebft. &ldquo;Nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd mua th\u00eam ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi, ch\u00fang ta h\u00e3y ch\u1edd xem nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y ra. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd b\u1ed5 sung l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0 Gareth Bale.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Sau nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec thay \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1ec1 m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. B\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n, l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9, v\u00e0 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea1t t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c theo c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, v\u00e0 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ebd \u0111em v\u1ec1 trong phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8. Khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi ai \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd bi\u1ebft.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tottenham kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn Gareth Bale\" title=\"Bale s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh khi Ronaldo ra \u0111i\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/HLV-Lopetegui-quyet-khong-de-Gareth-Bale-roi-Real-Madrid--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Tottenham kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn Gareth Bale</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Gareth Bale s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u1edf l\u1ea1i Real Madrid. K\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Premier League \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i trong kho\u1ea3ng 2 tu\u1ea7n n\u1eefa. Nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 bom t\u1ea5n, v\u00ec v\u1eady s\u1ebd l\u00e0 h\u01a1i mu\u1ed9n \u0111\u1ec3 k\u00edch n\u1ed5. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Man United c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8, v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 mong ch\u1edd th\u00eam 1 trung v\u1ec7 n\u1eefa.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tottenham kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn Gareth Bale v\u00e0 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111em v\u1ec1 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng quan tr\u1ecdng, khi h\u1ecd v\u1eabn ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/bale-quyet-dinh-hoan-le-cuoi-vi-ong-bo-vo-bat-hao-188-191842.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/23/bale-quyet-dinh-hoan-le-cuoi-vi-ong-bo-vo-bat-hao.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/hau-truong/bale-quyet-dinh-hoan-le-cuoi-vi-ong-bo-vo-bat-hao-188-191842.html\">Bale quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ho\u00e3n l\u1ec5 c\u01b0\u1edbi v\u00ec \u00f4ng b\u1ed1 v\u1ee3 b\u1ea5t h\u1ea3o</span><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh Gareth Bale c\u1ee7a Real Madrid ho\u00e3n \u0111\u00e1m c\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1edbi n\u0103m sau ch\u1ec9 v\u00ec Emma Rhys-Jones c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft vi\u1ec7c gia \u0111\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-khong-co-kha-nang-chieu-mo-gareth-bale-vi-tien-luong-172-191761.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/1/mu-khong-co-kha-nang-chieu-mo-gareth-bale-vi-tien-luong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-khong-co-kha-nang-chieu-mo-gareth-bale-vi-tien-luong-172-191761.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! L\u00fd do ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Gareth Bale?</span><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng MU mua Gareth Bale th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao b\u1edfi h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4790","checkdouble":"192272"},{"date":"23:01 29/07","title":"V\u1ee3 ch\u1ed3ng Morata ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n c\u1eb7p song sinh c\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e1ng y\u00eau","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/29/vo-chong-morata-chao-don-cap-song-sinh-cuc-dang-yeu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea \u2013 Alvaro Morata ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n c\u1eb7p song sinh Alessandro v\u00e0 Leonardo.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nMorata l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap n\u01a1i h\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 vui m\u1eebng th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i Instagram, v\u1ee3 ch\u1ed3ng anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n 2 ch\u00fa nh\u00f3c xinh x\u1eafn v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u Ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt (gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Alvaro Morata cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;V\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng ng\u00e0y n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ebfn &ndash; 29/7/2018, m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd qu\u00ean. Kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 d\u00e0i. D\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 9 th\u00e1ng nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, th\u1eddi gian c\u1ee9 nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 3 n\u0103m. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u1eddi n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 di\u1ec5n t\u1ea3 s\u1ef1 bi\u1ebft \u01a1n v\u1edbi Alice, c\u1ea3m \u01a1n em v\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 trao cho anh m\u00f3n qu\u00e0 tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng kinh ng\u1ea1c nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;M\u00f4i ng\u00e0y k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi quen em, anh lu\u00f4n c\u1ea3m \u01a1n Ch\u00faa v\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ta \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi nhau, em l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a anh. Nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y qua, em \u0111\u00e3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t con s\u01b0 t\u1eed c\u00e1i, v\u00e0 anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o h\u01a1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1eefa. Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00eam trong b\u1ec7nh vi\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng nhau r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec1u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00e0 th\u1eadt \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u1ee3 ch\u1ed3ng Morata ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n c\u1eb7p song sinh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/vo-chong-morata-chao-don-cap-song-sinh-cuc-dang-yeu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>V\u1ee3 ch\u1ed3ng Morata ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n c\u1eb7p song sinh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00e0o m\u1eebng 2 con \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi tr\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5t n\u00e0y, Alessandro v\u00e0 Leonardo. Cha ch\u1ec9 hy v\u1ecdng c\u00e1c con s\u1ebd th\u1eadt kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 ng\u1eadp tr\u00e0n t\u00ecnh y\u00eau th\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00edt th\u1edf b\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed trong c\u0103n nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta, m\u00e1i \u1ea5m c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n t\u1edbi c\u00e1c b\u00e1c s\u0129, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap ch\u00fang t\u00f4i tr\u1ea3i qua kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c trong b\u1ec7nh vi\u1ec7n Angelo. Xin c\u1ea3m \u01a1n l\u00f2ng t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c c\u1ee7a m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi!&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>C\u00f9ng xem nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Alvaro Morata ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n c\u1eb7p song sinh<br>\r\n</strong> <br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/alice.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Alice \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t c\u1ea1n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/morata.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Morata vui m\u1eebng ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n 2 thi\u00ean th\u1ea7n nh\u1ecf</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chua-co-bom-tan-hlv-sarri-van-hy-vong-bom-xit-morata-toa-sang-172-192227.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/22/chua-co-bom-tan-hlv-sarri-van-hy-vong-bom-xit-morata-toa-sang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chua-co-bom-tan-hlv-sarri-van-hy-vong-bom-xit-morata-toa-sang-172-192227.html\">Ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 bom t\u1ea5n, HLV Sarri v\u1eabn hy v\u1ecdng bom x\u1ecbt Morata t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng</span><br>\r\nCh\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Chelsea trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, HLV Sarri hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o Morata s\u1ebd th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-dan-dau-cuoc-dua-gianh-higuain-172-192257.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/chelsea-dan-dau-cuoc-dua-gianh-higuain.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-dan-dau-cuoc-dua-gianh-higuain-172-192257.html\">Chelsea chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Higuain</span><br>\r\nChelsea d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh Higuain. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc AC Milan d\u00f9 c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Juventus.</div>\r\n</div>\r\nNguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4789","checkdouble":"192274"},{"date":"23:35 29/07","title":"Sao M.U ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi mua b\u1edfi Napoli","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2017/11/30/sao-mu-chinh-thuc-duoc-hoi-mua-boi-napoli.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Aurelio De Laurentiis x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Napoli h\u1ecfi mua Darmian \u2013 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Man United.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nNapoli li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Darmian<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c Mourinho x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Italia, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Matteo Darmian d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u1edf Old Trafford. Ch\u00ednh anh c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, \u0111ang xem x\u00e9t nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u1ee3p l\u00fd nh\u1ea5t sau khi li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb cho ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf Man United.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Serie A \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y, g\u1ed3m Juventus, Inter Milan v\u00e0 Napoli. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng Naples \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn c\u00f3 quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi Darmian.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110\u00fang v\u1eady, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u1ed1 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, k\u00e8m v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t. Tuy nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu M.U kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n 6 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c. Trong \u0111\u00f3, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 Benjamin Henrichs t\u1eeb Bayer Leverkusen, ho\u1eb7c Santiago Arias c\u1ee7a PSV.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\" Napoli h\u1ecfi mua Darmian c\u1ee7a M.U\" title=\"Darmian cua MU\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/ngay-hom-nay-127.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>&nbsp;Napoli h\u1ecfi mua Darmian c\u1ee7a M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3n Darmian ra \u0111i, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd &ndash; \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u1ecd ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y. V\u1edbi ch\u00ednh h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Italia, anh c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 khi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn. B\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng, anh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n nay, Man United \u0111ang kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u00ean h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Antonio Valencia v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, v\u00e0 s\u1ebd ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Premier League. V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda t\u00e2n binh Diogo Dalot, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">2 c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u1ea3 d\u0129 kh\u00e1c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao ni\u1ec1m tin, ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng Ashley Young v\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 Victor Lindelof. D\u00f9 sao, Mourinho c\u0169ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb Napoli h\u1ecfi mua Darmian, n\u1ebfu \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh ti\u1ebfn tri\u1ec3n v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mac-mourinho-can-vien-doi-truong-mu-quyet-tam-ra-di-172-192213.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/mac-mourinho-can-vien-doi-truong-mu-quyet-tam-ra-di.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mac-mourinho-can-vien-doi-truong-mu-quyet-tam-ra-di-172-192213.html\">M\u1eb7c Mourinho c\u1ea7u vi\u1ec7n, &ldquo;\u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng&rdquo; MU quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ra \u0111i</span><br>\r\nH\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh Matteo Darmian l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh mong mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i ngay trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y nh\u1eb1m c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/valencia-dinh-chan-thuong-mu-khung-hoang-hau-ve-phai-172-192097.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/valencia-dinh-chan-thuong-mu-khung-hoang-hau-ve-phai.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/valencia-dinh-chan-thuong-mu-khung-hoang-hau-ve-phai-172-192097.html\">Valencia d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, M.U kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i</span><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf - h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Antonio Valencia d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y Premier League kh\u1edfi tranh.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4788","checkdouble":"192275"}]}